you'll miss the matinee.

1259
01:12:09,013 --> 01:12:11,843
It's okay with me.
One show a day is plenty.

1260
01:12:11,913 --> 01:12:14,402
To think I didn't
believe you at first, you dear--

1261
01:12:14,480 --> 01:12:19,276
