1285
01:13:59,480 --> 01:14:01,446
- The thing's breathing and living.
- Yes, it's true.

1286
01:14:01,480 --> 01:14:05,071
She's drab, but it's still
going to be a fine, fat hit.

1287
01:14:05,314 --> 01:14:07,677
- Mmm.
- Here's to your future...

1288
01:14:07,713 --> 01:14:10,770
as the new white knight
of the Great White Way.

