of success, you want to dump me
and go off with Helen Sinclair.

1325
01:16:16,447 --> 01:16:19,436
- That is ri-- That is ridiculous.
- Are you sure?

1326
01:16:19,513 --> 01:16:21,741
You know how crazy
you sound right now?

1327
01:16:21,813 --> 01:16:25,302
- You never encouraged me
to stay in Boston.
- I was submerged in my work.

1328
01:16:25,347 --> 01:16:28,438
