1409
01:20:56,380 --> 01:20:58,346
- Julian?
- Yeah?

1410
01:20:58,380 --> 01:21:00,845
- Did you hear about Olive?
- Oh, what now?

1411
01:21:00,913 --> 01:21:02,845
She got bumped off.

1412
01:21:04,646 --> 01:21:07,078
- What?
- Out at the docks.

1413
01:21:07,314 --> 01:21:09,541
A gangland hit.

1414
01:21:09,613 --> 01:21:12,670
- [ Door Slamming ]
- I wanna talk to you.

1415
01:21:12,746 --> 01:21:14,837
- Me?
- Yeah, you.

1416
01:21:14,913 --> 01:21:17,311
Hey, Joe.
Get lost for a while.

1417
01:21:17,380 --> 01:21:19,902
How could you?
How could you!

1418
01:21:19,980 --> 01:21:21,912
- Nobody's gonna ruin my play.
- Oh-- Your play?

1419
01:21:21,980 --> 01:21:24,810
- That's the second time
you called it your play.
- All right, our play.

1420
01:21:24,880 --> 01:21:28,472
- Didn't it cut you up inside
to hear her say it? Huh?
- We would've survived it!

1421
01:21:28,546 --> 01:21:31,979
Survived it? ls that what you want? When
